window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Britain, the not-too-distant future. Idir is taking the British Citizenship Test. He wants his family to belong.&nbsp;</p> <p>Twenty-five questions to determine his fate. Twenty-five chances to impress. When the test takes an unexpected and tragic turn, Idir is handed the power of life and death.&nbsp;</p> <p>How do you value a life when all you have is multiple choice?&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"; 
